# Deployment of Active Directory

I first installed VirtualBox and downloaded the ISO file for Windows Server 2022 from the Windows website. I checked the hash to verify its integrity.

I was able to install the server without issues.

I then set a static IP address of 192.168.10.1.

I added the Active Directory Domain Services role.

I promoted the server to a domain controller.

I verified that my lab.local domain appeared correctly in Active Directory Users and Computers.
